title: 'Body by Jake' Steinfeld Says Get Blood Pumping

description:
Jake Steinfeld, fitness icon and Chairman of Body by Jake Enterprises, discusses his creation of personal fitness training and how to stay in shape at home in quarantine.

Hosts: by Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Paul Brennan
